    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086940/extras/2f9658aa3e46a72b7fcb2a753aa39dc8.webp?t=1726250635\" width=616 height=60 /></span><br><br>Bass Defense combines musical rhythm-based gameplay with strategic elements. In Bass Defense's rhythm-based and action-packed 'Soundwave' game mode, you must hit the correct buttons in time with the music to clear your NMYs and save your base with the help of your upgradable power-ups or your sense of rhythm. Try your luck and 5 memorythms in this free episode.<br><br>NMYs don't like you.<br>NMYs want to destroy you.<br>NMYs attack you in forms of soundwaves.<br>NMYs are everywhere.<br>NMYs are part of the music.<br>NMYs are part of the rhythm.<br>NMYs are part of You.<br><br>Can you stay focused?<br>Can you clear them all?<br><strong>Can you save the base, with the help of ... <i>BASS</i>?</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086940/extras/d4b6e6ad681c5fc6bd193df682e1587f.webp?t=1726250635\" width=616 height=60 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Soundwave mode</h2>In this game mode, your objective is to save your base by using your upgradable - defensive or offensive - power-ups or your sense of rhythm. You have to be careful though - overusing your offensive power-ups might take you out of rhythm!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>rhythm-focused gameplay</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>you must hit the correct buttons in time with the music to clear your NMYs</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>top-down view</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>rhythm complexity, quantity <i>and</i> speed of NMYs vary by difficulty</li></ul><br>Additional game modes will be available in the full game - Bass Defense - Rhythm Meets Strategy .<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >5 unique levels</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>various challenges and visual styles</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>rhythm-sensitive, destructible objects</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>secrets and easter eggs</li></ul><br>Additional levels will be available in the full game - Bass Defense - Rhythm Meets Strategy.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >3 difficulties</h2>Find the perfect difficulty to match your skill level. Improve your sense of rhythm over time and try a harder difficulty!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086940/extras/351bd6418b17988b447cb8cb5de7e3ac.poster.avif?t=1726250635\" width=616 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086940/extras/351bd6418b17988b447cb8cb5de7e3ac.webm?t=1726250635\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086940/extras/351bd6418b17988b447cb8cb5de7e3ac.mp4?t=1726250635\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>chill, enjoy the music and casually clear some NMYs in <strong>Easy</strong> and <strong>Normal</strong> modes,</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>or challenge yourself in <strong>Hard</strong> mode, against more and much faster NMYs</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >4 power-ups</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086940/extras/3d2f8a026327aa85c95287fa2b541371.poster.avif?t=1726250635\" width=616 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086940/extras/3d2f8a026327aa85c95287fa2b541371.webm?t=1726250635\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086940/extras/3d2f8a026327aa85c95287fa2b541371.mp4?t=1726250635\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Additional power-ups will be available in the full game - Bass Defense - Rhythm Meets Strategy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086940/extras/fc227000fe0d0ee23124c0af98c85eb3.webp?t=1726250635\" width=616 height=60 /></span><br><br>You will definitely feel the law of conservation of energy, once you finish a long level on Hard difficulty: your kinetic energy turns into energy capsules! <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086940/extras/0d908c89401d98535e42a76a3367c399.webp?t=1726250635\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086940/extras/4b8360cfc899a2f6f4c9cc4f0508789f.webp?t=1726250635\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086940/extras/2227c3e7efc9c1fb09a93acd071b1156.webp?t=1726250635\" width=16 height=16 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>earn energy capsules by using your power-ups</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>distribute your hard-earned energy among your gear by upgrading them between levels and difficulties<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>yes ... <strong>you can reset your upgrades</strong> anytime!</li></ul></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>choose your own approach<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>plan your next strategy thoroughly,</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>or quickly try out your new setup</li></ul></li></ul>",
